Description:
Low maintenance single storey home in Metro Village
In the brilliantly designed Metro Village community where low maintenance housing meets practicality and a great location, this single storey home will please occupiers and investors alike. With Dandenong Creek and walking tracks at one end of the street, buses at the other and Dandenong train station all within walking distance, the home is ideally positioned to give you easy access to Eastlink, central Dandenong's shops, eateries and activities.
The home features gorgeous sparkling white tiling throughout and the bedrooms all carpeted for comfort. There are 3 robed bedrooms including the generous sized master with walk in wardrobe and a full ensuite. Walking further down the long hallway you will meet a huge tiled open plan lounge/dining zone that incorporates the huge kitchen with 600mm oven, 4 burner cooktop, plenty of cupboard / bench space and stainless steel appliances. Both sides of the dining room open via sliding doors to the concrete patio and compact and easily maintained backyard featuring grassed area, side gate and rainwater tanks for the garden.
Also featuring a central family bathroom, separate toilet, ducted gas heating, evaporative cooling so comfort is assured all year round, a double remote garage with internal access as well as a great functional laundry with external access.
This fantastic opportunity wont last long! Book your inspection today.

Description:
Luxury in an Architecturally Unique Home!
This architect designed home will take your breath away. Walk through the light filled spaces with their enormous windows bringing the private ornamental gardens in to the home.
Set on an easy to maintain block, the seclusion and security of the property takes you to another world, yet you are only a short distance to the city centre.
There are 3/4 bedrooms, enormous walk in robe to master, three bathrooms plus powder room, a fabulous kitchen with marble bench tops and quality appliances, oversized butlers pantry or second kitchen, two large living areas plus a formal dining room. There is extensive paving outside with space for entertaining around the BBQ.
The spectacular balcony reaches a landing that boasts North-Easterly views to the Dandenong Ranges. There is a double garage plus parking space off street for additional car, caravan or boat!
A sensational property with a lock and leave' configuration where you can head off on holidays knowing there is no maintenance required while you are away. An eye catching, individual home with beautiful clean lines, neutral tonings, high ceilings and expansive tiling.
Of course there is air conditioning, ducted heating and alarm system. Be impressed!

Contemporary Masterpiece !
This architect designed modern industrial style home will take your breath away. Walk through the light filled spaces with enormous windows which bring the private ornamental gardens in to the home.

Description:
Allagents-Allbuyers-Allaccess: Perfect 10 for Future Prospects
It’s not often you find a home like this. It’s the epitome of central Dandenong, but away from the hustle and bustle.
This solid brick home has been immaculately maintained over the years and is ripe for any investor, families or renovators.
The front wing consists of the open living that flows into the meals and kitchen which spills out to an undercover alfresco and spacious rear yard while the other wing of the home has three big bedrooms, two bathrooms. Boasting shutters, ornate cornices, high ceilings, massive laundry, ducted heating, evaporative cooling, an oversized lock up garage, workshop, 2nd kitchen with plumbing/gas plus a split system unit - this solid home on approximately 609m2 has it all!
Walk to Dandenong Central - life could not get any easier than this. the shopping arcades and food hub, Dandenong High School, Dandenong Market, bus stops, the updated train station - everything is at your fingertips!
A home like this ticks the boxes for all comers. Families can comfortably make the move and enjoy a solid secure lifestyle. Investors will love the premium position that’s so handy for tenants. Plus renovators can then this gem into a diamond or alternatively there’s potential for future development (STCA).
It’s versatile and in one of the best pockets of Dandenong, so call Mehmet Atesel ASAP.
Although all the care has gone into the marketing please only use as a guide and if need be do your own investigations. All Access RE Team
If your an Agent in Victoria and wish to refer a buyer please send us enquiry to register your buyer or give us a call.

Golden Development Opportunity (STCA)
This well-loved residence on a massive block of approximately 793m2 is a golden investment opportunity. Ready for a new lease on life, this property is looking for developers and investors with big plans!
What about the location you ask? Simply brilliant! Description:
Auction this Saturday at 11.00am
A home for those that expect nothing less than the best, 1 Amico Walk embodies premium family living at its finest. Generously proportioned, elegantly styled this grand family home will leave you breathless.
Positioned on a corner block in a quiet cul-de-sac, the home's commanding facade greets guests and residents with a hint of the luxury to follow. A double door entry opens up into the formal entrance with gorgeous Tasmanian Oak flooring, coffered ceilings and modern downlights. On the right is a substantial living space ideal for large gathering or split into a formal living and dining space. To the left is the downstairs master bedroom suite with walk in robe and private ensuite. A guest powder room and large laundry are well-positioned in the centre of the home whilst an open plan kitchen, meals and living area opens up the back of the ground floor. The gourmet kitchen and walk in pantry are a dream for both everyday family meals and larger festive feasts. A 5-burner gas cooktop, 900mm wide underbench oven and dishwasher are set within stylish stone benchtops and sleek cabinetry.
A modern timber staircase leads to the generous upstairs living and front balcony with views across the locale. Four bedrooms and three bathrooms complete the first floor; a substantial second master bedroom with lavish ensuite and walk in robe, a guest bedroom with built in robe and ensuite plus two additional robed bedrooms that share a double vanity bathroom and separate powder room.
This home truly has everything you could want and a list of extras so long you need to see it to truly appreciate it all. An alarm and intercom provide security and peace of mind, ducted heating and refrigerated cooling offer instant comfort and a double garage to the rear adds secure parking to the home.
Bi-fold doors, sliding doors and glazed walls merge outdoor and indoor living spaces for versatile and modern living. An enclosed alfresco with second kitchen flows through to the paved rear yard with easy care garden beds and double gate side access.
Enjoy outdoor open space at the end of Amico Walk, stroll to the playground and parklands adjacent Keshava Grove, choose from a range of schools just minutes away, follow Dandenong Creek to the town centre and explore the fabulous markets, shops, restaurants, cafes and public transport or jump on the Dandenong Bypass, Princes Highway or Eastlink for easy commuting.

Description:
THE CENTRE OF ATTENTION!
Comes with 4 bedrooms plus 3 separate living areas on Land Approx. 635m2 (Zoned Residential Growth- GRZ1) only minutes' walk to Dandenong Shopping Plaza!
Character, space and location defines this amazing property with its distinctive façade and picturesque front garden. Inside high ceilings and decorative plaster work complete with picture. This large home has 4 bedrooms (one upstairs), 3 separate living areas: a downstairs living room, a large family room which adjoins the kitchen plus an upstairs rumpus room.
Position Perfect: Only a few minutes' walk to the Dandenong Plaza Shopping Centre with the iconic Dandenong Market nearby, various schools, restaurants, medical facilities- you name it, all close to hand. Maybe you are thinking of future development? (STCA).
This one demands your attention! Your Call!

Description:
soldAS - My signs are everywhere
Brand new and just for you, this two storey townhouse’s striking architecture and chic interiors are set to impress.
Gorgeous timber style flooring, luxurious stone benchtops and high ceilings flow throughout the ground floor. Comprising of a study/sitting room at the front of the home, a central European laundry and powder room and at the rear an open plan kitchen, dining and living space. Upstairs you will find a generous master bedroom with walk in robe and private ensuite, two additional robed bedrooms and a stylish family bathroom. Bonus extras include ducted heating, air conditioner, LED downlights, stainless steel appliances and blinds throughout.
Residents will also enjoy a private courtyard with covered rear porch, timber deck, Astro Turf lawn, storage shed and a single garage plus additional tandem parking space.
Attracting first home buyers, families and investors, it is paired with a quiet cul-de-sac position walking distance to sporting amenities, playground and 5 local schools, nearby South Eastern Private Hospital and Oakwood Park, just minutes to the convenient shopping and lifestyle amenities of Dandenong CBD and with excellent transport options including Yarraman Train Station, Eastlink and Princes Highway.
• Brand new townhouse in quiet cul-de-sac position – ideal for first home buyers, families and investors
• Sitting room, open plan kitchen, dining and living area, three robed bedrooms, two bathrooms, powder room and European laundry
• Ducted heating, air conditioner, high ceilings, LED downlights, timber style flooring, stone benchtops, stainless steel appliances and blinds throughout
• Private courtyard with covered rear porch, timber deck, Astro Turf lawn, storage shed, single garage and tandem parking space
• Nearby 5 schools, sporting amenities, hospital, Dandenong CBD, train station, Eastlink and Princes Highway
